					<div class="stl_01" style="left:16.5em;top:2.1145em;"><span class="stl_46 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.71em;">(1) </span><span class="stl_42 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.71em;">Deliberate the purchase, exchange, lease, or value of real &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="left:16.5em;top:3.3645em;"><span class="stl_42" style="word-spacing:0.22em;">property at certain locations related to the relocation of 311, 911, and &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="left:16.5em;top:4.552em;"><span class="stl_42 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.76em;">emergency operations because deliberation in an open meeting &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="left:16.5em;top:5.7395em;"><span class="stl_42 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.38em;">would have a detrimental effect on the position of the governmental &nbsp;</span></div>
					<div class="stl_01" style="left:16.5em;top:6.927em;"><span class="stl_42 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.36em;">body in negotiations with a third person; and </span><span class="stl_46" style="word-spacing:0.31em;">(2) </span><span class="stl_42 stl_09" style="word-spacing:0.35em;">seek the advice of &nbsp;</span></div>
